---
import CloudinaryImage from './CloudinaryImage.astro';
---

<footer class="bg-secondary-bg py-24 px-6 md:px-12 border-t border-secondary-text/10">
  <div class="max-w-[1440px] mx-auto">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-8 lg:gap-16 mb-20">
      <!-- Brand Column -->
      <div class="reveal-up col-span-2 md:col-span-1">
        <a href="/" aria-label="InuWood - Acasă" class="inline-block mb-6">
          <CloudinaryImage
            src="/logo.png"
            alt="InuWood"
            width={160}
            height={64}
            class="h-16 w-auto object-contain"
            loading="lazy"
          />
        </a>
        <p class="text-sm text-primary-text/60 leading-relaxed max-w-[220px]">
          Mobilier din lemn masiv realizat manual cu tehnici tradiționale de tâmplărie în Bacău, România.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Sub-column 1 -->
      <div class="reveal-up" style="transition-delay: 100ms;">
        <h4 class="util-label text-accent mb-8 pb-2 border-b border-secondary-text inline-block">
          Navigare
        </h4>
        <nav aria-label="Footer navigation">
          <ul class="flex flex-col gap-4 text-sm font-medium text-primary-text/70">
            <li><a href="/" class="hover:text-accent transition-colors">Acasă</a></li>
            <li><a href="/about" class="hover:text-accent transition-colors">Despre Noi</a></li>
            <li><a href="/products" class="hover:text-accent transition-colors">Produse</a></li>
            <li><a href="/blog" class="hover:text-accent transition-colors">Blog</a></li>
            <li><a href="/contact" class="hover:text-accent transition-colors">Contact</a></li>
          </ul>
        </nav>
      </div>

      <!-- Sub-column 2 -->
      <div class="reveal-up" style="transition-delay: 200ms;">
        <h4 class="util-label text-accent mb-8 pb-2 border-b border-secondary-text inline-block">
          Urmărește-ne
        </h4>
        <ul class="flex flex-col gap-4 text-sm font-medium text-primary-text/70">
          <li><a href="https://instagram.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="hover:text-accent transition-colors" aria-label="Instagram">Instagram</a></li>
          <li><a href="https://pinterest.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="hover:text-accent transition-colors" aria-label="Pinterest">Pinterest</a></li>
          <li><a href="https://linkedin.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="hover:text-accent transition-colors" aria-label="LinkedIn">LinkedIn</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Sub-column 3 -->
      <div class="reveal-up" style="transition-delay: 300ms;">
        <h4 class="util-label text-accent mb-8 pb-2 border-b border-secondary-text inline-block">
          Atelier
        </h4>
        <address class="not-italic flex flex-col gap-4 text-sm font-medium text-primary-text/70">
          <p>Str. Meșteșugului nr. 24<br />Bacău, BC 600001<br />România</p>
          <p class="mt-2">
            <a href="mailto:contact@inuwood.ro" class="hover:text-accent transition-colors"
              >contact@inuwood.ro</a
            ><br />
            <a href="tel:+40753481013" class="hover:text-accent transition-colors">+40 753 481 013</a>
          </p>
        </address>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="border-t border-secondary-text/10 pt-8 flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-4">
      <p class="text-xs text-primary-text/50 font-medium">
        &copy; {new Date().getFullYear()} InuWood. Toate drepturile rezervate.
      </p>
      <p class="text-xs text-primary-text/50 font-medium">
        Meșteșugit cu pasiune în Bacău, România.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
